Your dialogue.

306
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:40,520
Liar.

307
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,560
You're cunning.

308
00:28:43,800 --> 00:28:45,320
You're cunning.

309
00:28:46,160 --> 00:28:47,920
You think I'm not on to you?

310
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,560
You think I'm not on to you?

311
