445
00:36:34,240 --> 00:36:35,560
You wanna try?

446
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:41,440
Yes.

447
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,000
Thank you.

448
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:45,800
