477
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:08,440
You're right.

478
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:12,600
Because I'll definitely pair off with Dr. Fahlada.

479
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:22,600
You're very confident.

480
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,160
Of course I am.

481
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:28,160
The doctor is good-looking,
talented and rich.

482
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:29,640
