527
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:12,120
I just didn't want to waste their time.

528
00:42:12,120 --> 00:42:15,040
Good. Now you know I hate you.

529
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,600
I despise you.

530
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:17,600
Fine.

531
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,720
