540
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:11,920
It's okay, Engfah.

541
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,520
I don't want trouble.

542
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:15,880
Okay.

543
00:43:17,520 --> 00:43:18,640
Let's leave.

544
00:43:19,200 --> 00:43:20,440
Okay.

545
00:43:20,480 --> 00:43:22,920
If you wanna leave, I'll leave.

546
00:43:42,720 --> 00:43:44,960
I already paid. Let's go.

547
00:43:47,600 --> 00:43:48,880
I'm off, Doctor.

548
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,280
When there's a chance,

549
00:43:50,760 --> 00:43:51,960
