552
00:44:19,360 --> 00:44:20,880
I couldn't help laughing.

553
00:44:21,320 --> 00:44:23,480
Did you overdo it?

554
00:44:23,600 --> 00:44:26,680
Jeez, she doesn't get people like us.

555
00:44:27,520 --> 00:44:30,640
