559
00:44:40,560 --> 00:44:43,440
And what about the person who got you wet?

560
00:44:43,840 --> 00:44:45,520
You want me to get her?

561
00:44:46,240 --> 00:44:47,800
That one's not smart either.

562
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:51,400
I already took care of her.

563
00:44:58,640 --> 00:44:59,840
-Let's go.
-Yes.

564
00:45:12,840 --> 00:45:14,840
A faucet in the bathroom broke.

565
00:45:15,120 --> 00:45:16,120
It got me wet.

566
00:45:19,280 --> 00:45:20,680
A bad faucet...

567
00:45:21,680 --> 00:45:22,920
or bad manners?

568
00:45:24,040 --> 00:45:25,040
What's that?

569
00:45:29,040 --> 00:45:30,080
Check, please.

570
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:34,400
It was already paid.

571
00:45:34,520 --> 00:45:35,640
By who?

572
00:45:35,880 --> 00:45:37,160
Ms. Engfah.

573
00:45:37,160 --> 00:45:39,400
She asked me to tell you it was her treat.

574
00:45:50,640 --> 00:45:51,880
I forgot my cellphone.

575
00:45:52,520 --> 00:45:54,040
Huh? Cellphone?

576
00:46:20,080 --> 00:46:21,080
Mm.

577
00:46:24,240 --> 00:46:25,240
Ah.

578
00:46:25,680 --> 00:46:26,680
There it is.

579
00:46:27,080 --> 00:46:28,240
My cellphone.

580
00:46:31,200 --> 00:46:32,200
Mm.

581
00:46:34,560 --> 00:46:35,680
Doc?

582
00:46:37,720 --> 00:46:39,680
Did you come for just your cellphone?

583
00:46:41,200 --> 00:46:42,200
Mm.

584
00:46:43,040 --> 00:46:44,040
That's right.

585
00:46:52,240 --> 00:46:53,960
Can't you stay for a little longer?

586
00:46:54,560 --> 00:46:55,560
Hm?

587
00:46:57,640 --> 00:46:58,640
Hm?

588
00:47:01,840 --> 00:47:02,840
Hm?

589
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:05,000
Please.

590
00:47:08,880 --> 00:47:10,320
Why do you want me to?

591
00:47:16,760 --> 00:47:19,160
Well, to accompany me.

592
00:47:19,320 --> 00:47:21,600
Just for a little while. It won't take long.

593
00:47:22,720 --> 00:47:24,120
Unless...

594
00:47:24,600 --> 00:47:26,360
you don't trust yourself.

595
00:47:27,000 --> 00:47:29,480
<i>♪ I want to say that I love you ♪</i>

596
00:47:29,480 --> 00:47:32,200
<i>♪ Love you with all my heart ♪</i>

597
00:47:32,240 --> 00:47:35,800
<i>♪ You don't need a single word ♪</i>

598
00:47:35,840 --> 00:47:38,840
<i>♪ To tell me how much you love me ♪</i>

599
00:47:38,840 --> 00:47:42,200
<i>♪ Your actions let me know ♪</i>

600
00:47:42,200 --> 00:47:46,360
<i>♪ I want us to stay this way ♪</i>

601
00:47:46,360 --> 00:47:48,640
<i>♪ No matter how tired we are ♪</i>

602
00:47:48,680 --> 00:47:51,600
<i>♪ Our hearts are ready to fight ♪</i>

603
00:47:51,600 --> 00:47:54,840
<i>♪ Just seeing love in our eyes ♪</i>

604
00:47:54,880 --> 00:47:59,880
<i>♪ Is enough to make us happy ♪</i>

605
00:48:01,240 --> 00:48:02,560
Hey! Hey!

606
00:48:02,560 --> 00:48:04,600
-Where are you hurt?
-Take her to a hospital!

607
00:48:04,640 --> 00:48:06,800
Calm down.
Our doctor will take care of her.

608
00:48:06,840 --> 00:48:08,360
It's gonna hurt a little.

609
00:48:08,360 --> 00:48:10,200
But I wanna keep getting hurt.

610
00:48:10,200 --> 00:48:12,720
-Why?
-So you pay attention to me.

611
00:48:12,880 --> 00:48:14,640
I heard when you were abroad,

612
00:48:14,640 --> 00:48:17,280
you and Earn lived together?

613
00:48:17,280 --> 00:48:18,720
Did Earn tell you that?

614
00:48:18,720 --> 00:48:20,840
Who do you think told me?

615
00:48:20,840 --> 00:48:23,600
Did she tell you
what we'd lived together as?

616
00:48:23,600 --> 00:48:24,600
She did.

617
00:48:24,600 --> 00:48:26,160
She said you were friends.

618
00:48:36,960 --> 00:48:41,680
<i>♪ Please don't let go of my hand ♪ </i>

619
00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:47,680
<i>♪ No matter what, please be right here ♪ </i>

620
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:52,080
<i>♪ Having you here is reassuring ♪ </i>

621
00:48:52,200 --> 00:48:55,560
<i>♪ I'm less anxious than I used to be ♪ </i>

622
00:48:56,600 --> 00:49:02,920
<i>♪ You're the good love I never experienced ♪ </i>
